com.xilinx.rapidwright.design

Class RelocatableTileRectangle

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.TileRectangle
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.RelocatableTileRectangle

  • public class RelocatableTileRectangle
extends TileRectangle
    A TileRectangle that is relocatable.

    As padding tiles may be inserted when relocating Rectangles, we do not store coordinates of tiles but rather the tiles themselves. For every border (top/bottom/left/right) we save one example tile. When Relocation is not needed, use SimpleTileRectangle instead
